OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to man who died in
OL,4,CBeaumont Leys Park
OL,6,FThe family of a man who died after
OL,7,Fbeing found unconscious at a park in
OL,8,FLeicester have paid tribute to him.
OL,10,FJames McKeown, also known as Jimmy,
OL,11,Fwas found at Beaumont Leys Park
OL,12,Fyesterday (Monday 6 April) evening. He
OL,13,Fwas taken to hospital and died a short
OL,14,Ftime after.
OL,16,FJames' family have issued a statement
OL,17,Fsaying that the events have "changed
OL,18,Ftheir lives forever"
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
