OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1775646168
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to man who died in
OL,4,CBeaumont Leys Park
OL,6,FThey said that "We have lost a loving
OL,7,Ffather, brother, partner and
OL,8,Fgrandfather, our lives will never be
OL,9,Fthe same again.
OL,11,F"Jimmy has lived locally for nearly 20
OL,12,Fyears and was well known in the
OL,13,Fcommunity, affectionately known to
OL,14,Fmany as Spider.
OL,16,F"We would ask that people respect our
OL,17,Fprivacy and give us the time to come
OL,18,Fto terms with what has happened."
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
