OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1775646168
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to man who died in
OL,4,CBeaumont Leys Park
OL,6,FA 33-year-old man was arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murder and remains in
OL,8,Fpolice custody.
OL,10,FDetective Inspector Kevin Hames from
OL,11,FEast Midlands Murder Investigation
OL,12,FTeam, said: "This is an extremely
OL,13,Fdifficult time for Jimmy's family and
OL,14,Fspecialist officers continue to
OL,15,Fsupport them.
OL,17,F"If you have any information about the
OL,18,Fincident, or the circumstances leading
OL,19,Fup to it, and have not yet spoken with
OL,20,Fofficers, we would ask that you get in
OL,21,Ftouch."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
